2557  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2558  [return: NotNull]
2559  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId);
2560 
2566  [return: NotNull]
2567  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8([NotNull] string str)
2568  {
2569  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2570  {
2571  return IntPtr.Zero;
2572  }
2573 
2574  IntPtr mem = INTERNAL_SDL_malloc(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0').Length);
2575  Marshal.Copy(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0'), 0, mem, Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0').Length);
2576  return mem;
2577  }
2578 
2585  public static int ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId)
2586  {
2587  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2588  {
2589  flags = messageBoxData.flags,
2590  window = messageBoxData.window,
2591  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.title),
2592  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.message),
2593  numbuttons = messageBoxData.numbuttons
2594  };
2595 
2596  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageBoxData.numbuttons];
2597  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2598 
2599  try
2600  {
2601  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2602  {
2603  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2604  {
2605  flags = messageBoxData.buttons[i].flags,
2606  buttonId = messageBoxData.buttons[i].buttonId,
2607  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.buttons[i].text)
2608  };
2609  }
2610 
2611  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2612  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
2613  {
2614  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
2615  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
2616  }
2617 
2618  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
2619 
2620  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2621  if (messageBoxData.colorScheme != null)
2622  {
2623  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
2624  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageBoxData.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
2625  }
2626 
2627  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonId);
2628 
2629  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2630  {
2631  INTERNAL_SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2632  }
2633 
2634  INTERNAL_SDL_free(data.message);
2635  INTERNAL_SDL_free(data.title);
2636 
2637  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2638  {
2639  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
2640  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
2641  }
2642 
2643  return result;
2644  }
2645  finally
2646  {
2647  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2648  {
2649  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
2650  }
2651  }
2652  }

7058  [return: NotNull]
7059  private static uint SdlDefinePixelFormat(PixelType type, [NotNull] uint order, PackedLayout layout, [NotNull] byte bits, [NotNull] byte bytes) => (uint) ((1 << 28) | ((byte) type << 24) | ((byte) order << 20) | ((byte) layout << 16) | (bits << 8) | bytes);
7060 
7066  [return: NotNull]
7067  private static byte SdlPixelFlag([NotNull] uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
7068 
7074  [return: NotNull]
7075  private static byte SdlPixelType([NotNull] uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
7076 
7082  [return: NotNull]
7083  private static byte SdlPixelOrder([NotNull] uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
7084 
7090  [return: NotNull]
7091  public static byte SdlPixelLayout([NotNull] uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
7092 
7098  [return: NotNull]
7099  public static byte SdlBitsPerPixel([NotNull] uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);
7100 
7106  [return: NotNull]
7107  public static byte SdlBytesPerPixel([NotNull] uint x)
7108  {
7109  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(x))
7110  {
7111  if (x == PixelFormatYuy2 ||
7112  x == PixelFormatUy ||
7113  x == PixelFormatYv)
7114  {
7115  return 2;
7116  }
7117 
7118  return 1;
7119  }
7120 
7121  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
7122  }
7123 
7129  [return: NotNull]
7130  public static bool IsPixelFormatIndexed([NotNull] uint format)
7131  {
7132  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
7133  {
7134  return false;
7135  }
7136 
7137  PixelType pType =
7138  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
7139  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex1 ||
7140  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex4 ||
7141  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex8;
7142  }
7143 
7149  [return: NotNull]
7150  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatPacked([NotNull] uint format)
7151  {
7152  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
7153  {
7154  return false;
7155  }
7156 
7157  PixelType pType =
7158  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
7159  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked8 ||
7160  pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked16 ||
7161  pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked32;
7162  }
7163 
7169  [return: NotNull]
7170  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatArray([NotNull] uint format)
7171  {
7172  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
7173  {
7174  return false;
7175  }
7176 
7177  PixelType pType =
7178  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
7179  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU8 ||
7180  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU16 ||
7181  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU32 ||
7182  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayF16 ||
7183  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayF32;
7184  }
7185 
7191  [return: NotNull]
7192  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatAlpha([NotNull] uint format)
7193  {
7194  if (SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(format))
7195  {
7196  PackedOrder pOrder =
7197  (PackedOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
7198  return pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderARgb ||
7199  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderRGba ||
7200  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderABgr ||
7201  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderBGra;
7202  }
7203 
7204  if (SdlIsPixelFormatArray(format))
7205  {
7206  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
7207  (SdlArrayOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
7208  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
7209  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
7210  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
7211  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
7212  }
7213 
7214  return false;
7215  }
7216 
7222  [return: NotNull]
7223  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatFour([NotNull] uint format) => (format == 0) && (SdlPixelFlag(format) != 1);

7657  [return: NotNull]
7658  public static bool SdlMustLock([NotNull]IntPtr surface)
7659  {
7660  SdlSurface sur = (SdlSurface) Marshal.PtrToStructure(
7661  surface,
7662  typeof(SdlSurface)
7663  );
7664  return (sur.flags & RleAccel) != 0;
7665  }
